Sir, is that really a priority right now?

42
00:02:42,890 --> 00:02:44,700
只要地球末日还没来临
Until such time as the world ends,

43
00:02:44,700 --> 00:02:47,190
我们就还要做好充足的准备
we will act as though it intends to spin on.

44
00:02:47,700 --> 00:02:49,400
清空地下的所有技术设备
Clear out the tech below.

45
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,890
把二阶的所有设备装车运走
Every piece of Phase 2 on a truck and gone.

46
00:02:51,890 --> 00:02:53,000
是  长官
Yes, sir.

47
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:54,490
跟我来
With me.

48
00:02:57,780 --> 00:02:59,130
博士  什么情况
Talk to me, Doctor.

49
00:03:00,610 --> 00:03:01,590
局长
Director.

50
00:03:02,130 --> 00:03:04,150
现在我们有确认的情况吗
Is there anything we know for certain?

51
00:03:04,150 --> 00:03:05,960
宇宙魔方乱动起来了
The Tesseract is misbehaving.

52
00:03:06,450 --> 00:03:09,190
-你在说笑吗  -这一点也不好笑
- Is that supposed to be funny? - No, it's not funny at all.

53
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:13,070
宇宙魔方不止被激活了  她还  自作主张
The Tesseract is not only active, she's behaving.

54
00:03:13,070 --> 00:03:14,310
你试过切断电源了吧
I assume you pulled the plug.

55
00:03:14,310 --> 00:03:16,240
她自身就是能量源
She's an energy source.

56
00:03:16,250 --> 00:03:19,020
我们关上电源  她能重新启动
We turn off the power, she turns it back on.

57
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,820
如果她的能量达到峰值
If she reaches peak level...

58
00:03:20,820 --> 00:03:22,580
我们为此做了准备  博士
We prepared for this, Doctor.

59
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:24,530
利用来自宇宙的能量
Harnessing energy from space.

60
00:03:24,530 --> 00:03:26,010
我们还没有掌控的能力
But we don't have the harness.

61
00:03:26,010 --> 00:03:27,830
我的计算还远没有完成
My calculations are far from complete.

62
00:03:27,830 --> 00:03:30,370
而现在她在释放干扰和辐射
And she's throwing off interference, radiation.

63
00:03:30,370 --> 00:03:32,810
没什么危害  只是低水平的伽马射线
Nothing harmful, low levels of gamma radiation.

64
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,770
那是能有危害的
That can be harmful.

65
00:03:35,180 --> 00:03:36,620
巴顿特工呢
Where's Agent Barton?

66
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:38,360
那只鹰吗
The Hawk?

67
00:03:39,380 --> 00:03:41,340
当然还是窝在巢里了
Up in his nest, as usual.

68
00:03:42,940 --> 00:03:44,690
巴顿特工  回话
Agent Barton, report.

69
00:03:45,590 --> 00:03:46,700
我让你负责安保
I gave you this detail

70
00:03:46,700 --> 00:03:48,460
是让你密切关注一切情况
so you could keep a close eye on things.

71
00:03:48,460 --> 00:03:50,380
我在高处看得更清楚
Well, I see better from a distance.

72
00:03:50,380 --> 00:03:52,750
那你看到是什么激活了魔方吗
Have you seen anything that might set this thing off?

73
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:54,670
博士  能量又激增了
Doctor, it's spiking again.

74
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:56,480
没有人进出
No one's come or gone.

75
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:58,140
塞尔维格没问题
And Selvig's clean.

76
00:03:58,440 --> 00:04:00,280
没与人接触或传递信息
No contacts, no IMs.

77
00:04:01,260 --> 00:04:02,330
如果有谁在搞鬼  长官
If there was any tampering, sir,

78
00:04:02,330 --> 00:04:03,750
也不是我们这边的人
it wasn't at this end.

79
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,520
什么意思
"At this end"?

80
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:10,130
魔方是通向宇宙另一端的门吧
Yeah, the Cube is a doorway to the other end of space, right?

81
00:04:12,170 --> 00:04:13,820
而门从两边都能开
Doors open from both sides.

82
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,580
还没到
Not yet.

83
00:05:23,590 --> 00:05:26,960
先生  请放下你的矛
Sir, please put down the spear.

84
00:06:05,900 --> 00:06:07,390
你挺勇敢[有心]
You have heart.

85
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:38,890
劝你不要
Please don't.

86
00:06:41,010 --> 00:06:42,520
我还需要它
I still need that.

87
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:44,220
没必要把事情闹得更大
This doesn't have to get any messier.

88
00:06:44,220 --> 00:06:45,420
当然有必要
Of course it does.

89
00:06:45,430 --> 00:06:47,830
我远道而来就是为了它
I've come too far for anything else.

90
00:06:49,310 --> 00:06:52,990
我是洛基  来自阿斯加德
I am Loki, of Asgard

91
00:06:52,990 --> 00:06:55,560
我肩负着光荣的使命
and I am burdened with glorious purpose.

92
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,630
洛基
Loki,

