We have no quarrel with your people.

95
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:04,710
就像蚂蚁也没有招惹靴子
An ant has no quarrel with a boot.

96
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:07,220
你的意思是要踩死我们吗
Are you planning to step on us?

97
00:07:07,220 --> 00:07:09,810
我带来了福音
I come with glad tidings

98
00:07:11,430 --> 00:07:13,730
我要帮你们摆脱束缚
of a world made free.

99
