你口口声声说安宁
Yeah, you say "Peace,"

105
00:07:32,380 --> 00:07:34,480
但我觉得你的意思正相反
I kind of think you mean the other thing.

106
00:07:34,490 --> 00:07:36,650
长官  弗瑞局长在拖延时间
Sir, Director Fury is stalling.

107
00:07:37,140 --> 00:07:38,940
这个地方就要爆炸了
This place is about to blow

108
00:07:38,940 --> 00:07:40,960
我们会被压在几十米的石头下
and drop a hundred feet of rock on us.

109
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:42,970
他想要埋葬我们
He means to bury us.

110
00:07:42,970 --> 00:07:44,500
就像古时的法老
Like the pharaohs of old.

111
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:46,740
他说得对  传送门正在自我塌陷
He's right. The portal is collapsing in on itself.

112
00:07:46,740 --> 00:07:49,470
再过两分钟就会达到极值
We've got maybe two minutes before this goes critical.

113
00:07:49,470 --> 00:07:50,530
那好吧
Well, then.

114
00:08:06,010 --> 00:08:07,450
我要用这些车
I need these vehicles.

115
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:13,450
-那是谁  -不知道
- Who's that? - They didn't tell me.

116
