希尔
Hill!

117
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,500
听得到吗
Do you copy?

118
00:08:20,130 --> 00:08:22,140
巴顿叛变了
Barton has turned.

119
00:08:34,660 --> 00:08:37,000
他们抢走了宇宙魔方  拦住他们
They have the Tesseract! Shut them down!

120
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:16,420
好了  走吧  别管了  快走
Okay, let's go. No, leave it. Go!

121
00:09:32,410 --> 00:09:34,680
楼上撤空了  长官  你得赶快离开
We're clear upstairs, sir. You need to go.

122
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,570
局长
Director?

123
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,980
弗瑞局长  听到了吗
Director Fury, do you copy?

124
00:11:10,110 --> 00:11:12,450
宇宙魔方被敌人抢走了
The Tesseract is with a hostile force.

125
00:11:12,450 --> 00:11:14,750
有人负伤  希尔你呢
I have men down. Hill?

126
00:11:15,150 --> 00:11:16,870
还有很多人被埋在地下
A lot of men still under.

127
00:11:17,310 --> 00:11:19,300
我不知道有多少幸存者
I don't know how many survivors.

128
00:11:19,300 --> 00:11:20,540
发出全面命令
Sound a general call.

129
00:11:20,540 --> 00:11:22,350
所有不参与救援的人员
I want every living soul not working rescue

130
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:23,840
去追查箱子的下落
looking for that briefcase.

131
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:24,780
明白
Roger that.

132
00:11:24,780 --> 00:11:28,150
科尔森  返回基地  这是7级事件
Coulson, get back to base. This is a Level Seven.

133
00:11:29,270 --> 00:11:30,760
现在
As of right now,

134
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:32,730
战争已经打响
we are at war.

135
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:35,240
我们该怎么办
What do we do?

136
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:49,480
{\an5}复仇者联盟

