184
00:15:48,030 --> 00:15:50,160
{\an2}{\pos(192,238)}他发烧了  还一直难受地呻吟

185
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:51,460
{\an2}{\pos(192,238)}但眼睛却睁不开

186
00:15:51,470 --> 00:15:52,570
{\an2}{\pos(192,238)}慢慢说

187
00:15:53,770 --> 00:15:55,240
{\an2}{\pos(192,238)}我爸爸

188
00:15:57,390 --> 00:15:58,580
{\an2}{\pos(192,238)}像他们一样吗

189
00:16:02,550 --> 00:16:03,660
求你了
Please.

190
00:16:30,940 --> 00:16:33,430
该先收钱的  班纳
You should've got paid up front, Banner.

191
00:16:33,430 --> 00:16:36,220
对于一个该远离压力的人来说
You know, for a man who's supposed to be avoiding stress

192
00:16:36,220 --> 00:16:38,730
你可真是选了一个好地方安居
you picked a hell of a place to settle.

193
00:16:41,370 --> 00:16:43,590
远离压力不是我的诀窍
Avoiding stress isn't the secret.

194
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:45,860
那是什么  做瑜伽吗
Then what is it? Yoga?

195
00:16:47,470 --> 00:16:49,990
你把我引到郊区来  真聪明
You brought me to the edge of the city. Smart.

196
00:16:51,180 --> 00:16:54,390
这里肯定被包围了吧
I assume the whole place is surrounded.

197
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:56,980
只有你和我
Just you and me.

198
00:16:58,380 --> 00:17:00,190
你那个小演员呢
And your actress buddy?

199
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:02,790
她也是间谍吗  入行还真早啊
Is she a spy, too? They start that young?

200
00:17:02,970 --> 00:17:03,940
我当年就是
I did.

201
00:17:04,390 --> 00:17:05,580
你是谁
Who are you?

202
00:17:05,580 --> 00:17:07,100
娜塔莎·罗曼诺夫
Natasha Romanoff.

203
00:17:10,130 --> 00:17:11,690
你是来杀我的吗  罗曼诺夫女士
Are you here to kill me, Ms Romanoff?

204
00:17:11,690 --> 00:17:14,130
因为那对所有人都不会有好结果的
Because that's not going to work out for everyone.

205
00:17:14,130 --> 00:17:17,300
不  当然不是  我是代表神盾局而来
No, of course not. I'm here on behalf of S.H.I.E.L.D.

206
00:17:18,900 --> 00:17:20,010
神盾局
S.H.I.E.L.D.

207
00:17:22,010 --> 00:17:23,280
他们怎么找到我的
How did they find me?

208
00:17:23,280 --> 00:17:24,590
我们一直掌握着你的行踪  博士
We never lost you, Doctor.

209
00:17:24,590 --> 00:17:26,190
只是一直保持着距离
We've kept our distance.

210
00:17:26,190 --> 00:17:29,300
甚至还替你甩掉了一些其他相关方
Even helped keep some other interested parties off your scent.

211
00:17:29,890 --> 00:17:31,020
为什么
Why?

212
00:17:31,020 --> 00:17:32,960
尼克·弗瑞还挺信任你
Nick Fury seems to trust you.

213
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:34,990
但现在你得跟我走
But now we need you to come in.

214
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,650
要是我不肯呢
What if I say no?

215
00:17:38,320 --> 00:17:39,780
我会说服你
I'll persuade you.

216
00:17:42,420 --> 00:17:46,260
要是...那个家伙不肯呢
And what if the other guy says no?

217
00:17:47,460 --> 00:17:49,160
你一年多没出过"事故"了
You've been more than a year without an incident.

218
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:51,360
我想你应该也不想破这个戒
I don't think you want to break that streak.

219
00:17:54,140 --> 00:17:56,450
我并不是总能如愿的
Well, I don't every time get what I want.

220
00:17:57,720 --> 00:18:00,580
博士  我们可能要迎来一场全球灾难
Doctor, we're facing a potential global catastrophe.

221
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:04,280
那是我一直在努力避免的
Well, those I actively try to avoid.

222
00:18:04,280 --> 00:18:05,350
这个
This

223
00:18:06,450 --> 00:18:08,160
是宇宙魔方
is the Tesseract.

224
00:18:08,890 --> 00:18:11,580
它有毁灭整个地球的能量
It has the potential energy to wipe out the planet.

225
00:18:14,800 --> 00:18:17,140
那弗瑞想要我做什么  把它吃掉吗
What does Fury want me to do, swallow it?

226
00:18:17,140 --> 00:18:19,950
他要你找到它  它被抢走了
He wants you to find it. It's been taken.

227
00:18:20,380 --> 00:18:24,290
它发出的伽马信号太弱  我们无法追踪
It emits a gamma signature that's too weak for us to trace.

228
00:18:24,740 --> 00:18:27,860
而你是最了解伽马射线的人了
There's no one that knows gamma radiation like you do.

229
00:18:27,860 --> 00:18:30,650
否则我也不会来找你
If there was, that's where I'd be.

230
00:18:31,260 --> 00:18:33,670
所以  弗瑞不是派你来抓怪物的咯
So, Fury isn't after the monster?

231
00:18:33,670 --> 00:18:35,190
反正他不是这么跟我说的
Not that he's told me.

232
00:18:35,190 --> 00:18:36,840
他什么都会跟你说吗
And he tells you everything?

233
00:18:38,020 --> 00:18:39,670
去跟弗瑞谈吧  他需要你的帮助
Talk to Fury. He needs you on this.

234
00:18:39,670 --> 00:18:40,690
他要把我关起来吗
He needs me in a cage?

235
00:18:40,700 --> 00:18:41,800
没有人会把你关起...
No one's going to put you in a...

236
00:18:41,810 --> 00:18:43,320
不要再骗我了
Stop lying to me!

237
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,960
抱歉  我不该这么凶
I'm sorry. That was mean.

238
00:18:50,650 --> 00:18:52,510
我就是想试探一下你
I just wanted to see what you'd do.

239
00:18:53,970 --> 00:18:57,140
这样吧  我们好好说话
Why don't we do this the easy way

240
00:18:57,140 --> 00:18:58,680
你把枪收起来
where you don't use that

241
00:18:58,680 --> 00:19:02,740
而我也确保那个家伙不会乱来
and the other guy doesn't make a mess.

242
00:19:03,370 --> 00:19:04,340
好吗
Okay?

243
00:19:05,690 --> 00:19:06,800
娜塔莎
Natasha?

244
00:19:12,600 --> 00:19:13,630
退后
Stand down.

245
00:19:14,660 --> 00:19:15,790
一切正常
We're good here.

246
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:19,300
还说"只有你和我"呢
"Just you and me."

247
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:24,130
这太过分了  局长
This is out of line, Director.

248
00:19:24,540 --> 00:19:27,040
你在摆弄你控制不了的力量
You're dealing with forces you can't control.

249
00:19:27,380 --> 00:19:31,040
你打过仗吗  理事先生  上过战场吗
You ever been in a war, Councilman? In a firefight?

250
00:19:31,040 --> 00:19:34,090
你那时觉得能完全掌控局面吗
Did you feel an overabundance of control?

251
00:19:34,090 --> 00:19:37,510
你是说这个阿斯加德已经向地球宣战了吗
You're saying that this Asgard is declaring war on our planet?

252
00:19:37,520 --> 00:19:40,400
不是阿斯加德  只是洛基
Not Asgard. Loki.

253
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,860
他不可能是单干  另一个神呢
He can't be working alone. What about the other one?

254
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:44,350
他哥哥
His brother.

255
00:19:44,360 --> 00:19:46,670
根据我们的情报  托尔不是敌人
Our intelligence says Thor is not a hostile

256
00:19:46,670 --> 00:19:48,060
但他离我们太远了
but he's worlds away.

257
00:19:48,060 --> 00:19:49,950
我们不能指望他来帮忙
We can't depend on him to help, either.

258
00:19:49,950 --> 00:19:50,890
我们只能靠自己
It's up to us.

259
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:53,820
所以你更应该全力开发二阶
Which is why you should be focusing on Phase 2.

260
00:19:53,820 --> 00:19:55,080
它正是为这种情况...
It was designed for exactly this...

261
00:19:55,080 --> 00:19:58,740
二阶还没完成  但敌人却准备好了
Phase 2 isn't ready. Our enemy is.

262
00:19:58,740 --> 00:20:00,470
我们需要一支应急小队
We need a response team.

263
00:20:00,470 --> 00:20:02,930
复仇者计划已被取消
The Avengers Initiative was shut down.

264
00:20:02,930 --> 00:20:04,690
我不是指复仇者联盟
This isn't about the Avengers.

265
00:20:04,690 --> 00:20:05,860
我们看过那份名单
We've seen the list.

266
00:20:05,870 --> 00:20:08,450
你有着世界一流的秘密特工组织
You're running the world's greatest covert security network

267
00:20:08,450 --> 00:20:10,310
却要把人类的命运交给
and you're going to leave the fate of the human race

268
00:20:10,310 --> 00:20:11,700
一群怪胎吗
to a handful of freaks.

269
00:20:11,710 --> 00:20:13,880
我没有要把任何事交给任何人
I'm not leaving anything to anyone.

270
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:16,380
我们确实需要一支应急小队
We need a response team.

271
00:20:16,380 --> 00:20:19,300
这些人或许孤僻  甚至不太正常
These people may be isolated, unbalanced even

272
00:20:19,300 --> 00:20:21,220
但我相信只要有正确的动力
but I believe with the right push

273
00:20:21,220 --> 00:20:23,880
他们就能成为我们需要的力量
they can be exactly what we need.

274
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:25,380
你相信吗
You believe?

275
00:20:25,380 --> 00:20:28,710
靠感情可赢不了战争  局长
War isn't won by sentiment, Director.

276
00:20:29,610 --> 00:20:32,910
是的  只能靠战士
No, it's won by soldiers.

277
00:20:52,420 --> 00:20:53,700
没时间了
There's not enough time.

278
00:20:54,630 --> 00:20:56,220
我得让飞机坠海
I got to put her in the water!

279
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:02,770
你不是一个人
You won't be alone.

280
00:21:03,020 --> 00:21:04,140
天啊
Oh, my God.

281
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:06,620
这家伙还活着
This guy is still alive!

282
00:21:30,930 --> 00:21:32,170
睡不着吗
Trouble sleeping?

283
00:21:33,940 --> 00:21:37,030
我睡了70年  长官  我想我睡得够久了
I slept for 70 years, sir. I think I've had my fill.

284
00:21:38,170 --> 00:21:39,700
那你该出去走走
Then you should be out,

285
00:21:39,700 --> 00:21:42,500
庆祝一下  看看世界
celebrating, seeing the world.

286
00:21:47,920 --> 00:21:50,700
我沉睡的时候  世界还在打仗
When I went under, the world was at war.

287
00:21:50,980 --> 00:21:52,910
等我醒来  他们说战争打赢了
I wake up, they say we won.

288
00:21:53,540 --> 00:21:55,360
却没说我们失去了什么
They didn't say what we lost.

289
00:21:55,740 --> 00:21:58,080
我们一路走来犯了些错误
We've made some mistakes along the way.

290
00:21:58,440 --> 00:22:00,580
有些就在不久之前
Some, very recently.

291
00:22:01,710 --> 00:22:02,910
你有任务要给我吗  长官
Are you here with a mission, sir?

292
00:22:02,910 --> 00:22:03,990
是的
I am.

293
00:22:04,130 --> 00:22:05,790
想让我回归这个世界吗
Trying to get me back in the world?

294
00:22:06,340 --> 00:22:07,750
是让你拯救世界
Trying to save it.

295
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:14,200
九头蛇的秘密武器
HYDRA's secret weapon.

296
00:22:13,270 --> 00:22:15,560
{\an8}宇宙魔方

297
00:22:14,820 --> 00:22:16,930
是霍华德·斯塔克在找你的时候
Howard Stark fished that out of the ocean

298
00:22:16,930 --> 00:22:18,800
从海底打捞上来的
when he was looking for you.

299
00:22:18,800 --> 00:22:20,680
他和我们想的一样
He thought what we think.

300
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:25,300
宇宙魔方是开发无限可再生能源的关键
The Tesseract could be the key to unlimited sustainable energy.

301
00:22:25,300 --> 00:22:28,430
这正是世界所迫切需要的
That's something the world sorely needs.

302
00:22:30,590 --> 00:22:31,950
它被谁抢走了
Who took it from you?

303
00:22:31,950 --> 00:22:33,370
他叫洛基
He's called Loki.

304
00:22:33,630 --> 00:22:36,130
他不是本地人
He's not from around here.

305
00:22:36,660 --> 00:22:39,930
你加入的话还有很多情况需要了解
There's a lot we'll have to bring you up to speed on if you're in.

306
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:43,390
这世界和你记忆中的比起来
The world has gotten even stranger

307
00:22:43,390 --> 00:22:44,760
变得更加奇怪了
than you already know.

308
00:22:44,760 --> 00:22:46,950
事到如今  我觉得已经没什么能让我意外了
At this point, I doubt anything would surprise me.

309
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:49,830
我赌10块钱  说你错了
Ten bucks says you're wrong.

310
00:22:51,330 --> 00:22:52,790
任务资料
There's a debriefing packet

311
00:22:52,790 --> 00:22:54,910
已经放在你公寓了
waiting for you back at your apartment.

312
00:22:57,620 --> 00:22:59,370
关于宇宙魔方
Is there anything you can tell us about the Tesseract

313
00:22:59,370 --> 00:23:01,260
你能告诉我们什么吗
that we ought to know now?

314
00:23:01,260 --> 00:23:02,940
你们就不该把它捞上来
You should have left it in the ocean.

315
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:39,290
这边准备就绪  接下来看你的了
Good to go on this end. The rest is up to you.

316
00:23:39,290 --> 00:23:40,790
你断开输电线了吗
You disconnected the transmission lines?

317
00:23:40,790 --> 00:23:41,900
我们与电网断开了吗
Are we off the grid?

318
00:23:41,910 --> 00:23:43,660
斯塔克大厦即将成为
Stark Tower is about to become a beacon

319
00:23:43,660 --> 00:23:45,870
自给清洁能源的灯塔
of self-sustaining clean energy.

320
00:23:45,870 --> 00:23:47,810
如果方舟反应堆能接替发电
Well, assuming the arc reactor takes over

321
00:23:47,820 --> 00:23:49,440
并且正常运行的话
and it actually works.

322
00:23:49,440 --> 00:23:50,550
应该没问题
I assume.

323
00:23:51,330 --> 00:23:52,310
开灯吧
Light her up.

324
00:23:56,040 --> 00:24:00,250
{\an8}斯塔克

325
00:23:58,080 --> 00:23:59,010
看起来怎么样
How does it look?

326
00:23:59,020 --> 00:24:01,940
像圣诞彩灯  但更有我的风格
Like Christmas, but with more me.

327
00:24:01,940 --> 00:24:03,780
我们得加大公众宣传
We've got to go wider on the public awareness campaign.

328
00:24:03,780 --> 00:24:05,570
你得在媒体上造势
You need to do some press.

329
00:24:05,570 --> 00:24:06,380
我明天去华盛顿
I'm in DC tomorrow,

330
00:24:06,380 --> 00:24:08,190
为另外三座大楼选址
I'm working on the zoning for the next three buildings.

331
00:24:08,190 --> 00:24:10,800
派珀  你把气氛都毁了  当下
Pepper, you're killing me. The moment, remember?

332
00:24:10,800 --> 00:24:12,050
要享受当下
Enjoy the moment.

333
00:24:12,050 --> 00:24:13,750
等你进来我再享受
Get in here and I will.

334
00:24:16,610 --> 00:24:20,020
先生  神盾局的科尔森特工打来电话
Sir, Agent Coulson of S.H.I.E.L.D. is on the line.

335
00:24:20,020 --> 00:24:20,970
说我在外面
I'm not in.

336
00:24:21,580 --> 00:24:23,030
我确实在外面
I'm actually out.

337
00:24:30,290 --> 00:24:32,540
先生  恐怕他坚持要找您
Sir, I'm afraid he's insisting.

338
00:24:33,090 --> 00:24:35,750
强硬点  贾维斯  我有约会
Grow a spine, Jarvis. I got a date.

339
00:24:40,320 --> 00:24:43,500
能量水平稳定...吧
Levels are holding steady, I think.

340
00:24:43,500 --> 00:24:45,920
当然了  是我亲自动手的
Of course they are. I was directly involved.

341
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:47,110
这正好让我想到一个问题
Which brings me to my next question.

342
00:24:47,110 --> 00:24:49,370
当天才的感觉如何
How does it feel to be a genius?

343
00:24:49,370 --> 00:24:51,930
我怎么会知道
Well, I really wouldn't know, now would I?

344
00:24:51,930 --> 00:24:56,010
这叫什么话  这一切都归功于你
What do you mean? All this came from you.

345
00:24:56,540 --> 00:24:59,790
不  这一切都归功于这个
No, all this came from that.

346
00:25:00,520 --> 00:25:02,840
别这么谦虚  拜托
Give yourself some credit. Please.

347
00:25:02,850 --> 00:25:04,850
斯塔克大厦就是你的孩子
Stark Tower is your baby.

348
00:25:04,850 --> 00:25:07,820
你有12%的功劳
Give yourself 12% of the credit.

349
00:25:08,180 --> 00:25:09,010
才12%
12%?

350
00:25:09,010 --> 00:25:10,300
商量一下可以升到15%
An argument can be made for 15.

351
00:25:10,310 --> 00:25:12,130
我的孩子我只有12%的份
12%? My baby?

352
00:25:12,130 --> 00:25:13,730
毕竟重活都是我干的
Well, I did do all the heavy lifting.

353
00:25:13,730 --> 00:25:16,010
都不是比喻  重物都是我搬的
Literally, I lifted the heavy things.

354
00:25:16,010 --> 00:25:18,500
而且  不好意思  安全漏洞怎么算
And, sorry, but the security snafu?

355
00:25:18,500 --> 00:25:20,100
该算在你头上
That was on you.

356
00:25:20,100 --> 00:25:21,810
-我的私人电梯  -你是说我们的电梯吧
- My private elevator... - You mean our elevator?

357
00:25:21,810 --> 00:25:24,610
挤满了一身臭汗的工人
...it was teeming with sweaty workmen.

358
00:25:25,120 --> 00:25:27,660
过会儿你会因为我说了占多少份这话
I'm going to pay for that comment about percentages

359
00:25:27,660 --> 00:25:29,700
而温柔地报复我  是吧
in some subtle way later, aren't I?

360
00:25:30,140 --> 00:25:31,610
没你想的那么温柔
It's not going to be that subtle.

361
00:25:31,620 --> 00:25:32,700
这样吧
I'll tell you what.

362
00:25:33,060 --> 00:25:35,570
我在下一栋大楼上写上你的名字
The next building is gonna say "Potts" on the tower.

363
00:25:35,580 --> 00:25:37,170
直接写在地契上吧
On the lease.

364
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:39,630
打电话问问你妈  你能留下过夜吗
Call your mom. Can you bunk over?

365
00:25:40,220 --> 00:25:41,800
先生  您的电话
Sir, the telephone.

366
00:25:41,800 --> 00:25:44,140
恐怕我的程序被人改写了
